OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSpread high energy costs   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover several years, says   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FOctopus Energy boss        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Spreading the cost of high gas prices  
OL,6, over a number of years is the best way 
OL,7, to deal with price spikes, the  boss of
OL,8, one of the UK's biggest energy firms   
OL,9, has said.                              
OL,11,FOctopus Energy's Greg Jackson said it  
OL,12,Fwas the only option able to "make a    
OL,13,Freal difference to all customers".     
OL,15,FSpreading the cost would mean consumers
OL,16,Fwould avoid hefty increases to their   
OL,17,Fenergy bills, he said.                 
OL,19,FEnergy costs are expected to jump in   
OL,20,FApril when the price cap is revised.   
